				<div class="dablink">This article is about the <a href="/wiki/Polynesian_languages" title="Polynesian languages">Polynesian</a> language of the kingdom of <a href="/wiki/Tonga" title="Tonga">Tonga</a>. For unrelated languages with similar names, see <a href="/wiki/Tongan_language_(disambiguation)" title="Tongan language (disambiguation)" class="mw-redirect">Tongan language (disambiguation)</a>.</div>
